%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^%^ULINE%^Lunar Mystery%^RESET%^

Moon-touched, your thoughts deviate from the norm and lead you on strange journeys.

%^BOLD%^CYAN%^Revelations:%^RESET%^
( 1) Claw and Tooth             : Gain Bite and Claw attacks
( 5) Primal Companion           : Summon an animal companion
(10) Prophetic Armor            : CHA to armor bonus instead of DEX
(15) Eye of the Moon            : Passive Darkvision
(21) Avatar of the Primal World : Gain all lycanthrope shape innate spells
(31) Final Revelation           : Heal/Cure stronger, Harm/Cause causes confusion

%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Class Skills%^RESET%^: athletics, perception, survival

%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Bonus Spells%^RESET%^: garble, dust of twilight, rage, aspect of the wolf, moonbeam, litany of madness, lunar veil, blood mist, polar midnight
